        days (big hurry?).
        now the  engine  supports  the following  object  primitives: plane,
        sphere and cylinder (quadrics support in progress). all of these can
        be texture  mapped. the illumination  model is true  Phong illumina-
        tion. first  time  generated  textures (great  turbulence  ideas  by
